snippet.title: Prehistoric Kingdom | Early Access Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/666150/Prehistoric_Kingdom/

Take control of limitless power in Prehistoric Kingdom to build, manage and grow the ultimate zoo for extinct animals - arriving Q2 2022 (ETA updated 27/08/2021).
